    <div class="body">
      What percent of their total BTC were in the hot wallet?  I thought the idea behind hot/cold wallets was so that only a small fraction of the total would be at risk so that in the event of an attack the organization would remain solvent and be able to recover its losses from future transaction fees protecting its users BTC.
      
    </div>
