        <span class="hidden-icon-start"></span>
        
      </aside>
    </header>
    <div class="body">
      <div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">The attacker then successfully exploited a flaw in the code which allows transfers between flexcoin users. By sending thousands of simultaneous requests, <span style="font-weight: bold">the attacker was able to</span> &quot;move&quot; coins from one user account to another until the sending account was overdrawn, before balances were updated.</div><br /><br />The bold part should instead read &quot;our shoddy code allowed anyone who poked around enough to&quot;.
      
    </div>
