    <span class="author" data-post-author="bh5505"><a href="http://arstechnica.com/civis/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=266456&amp;sid=bc0216a5256140675548100709fda8f2">bh5505</a></span><span class="rank">Smack-Fu Master, in training</span>
