  <header class="byline">
    
    <span class="author" data-post-author="pallentx"><a href="http://arstechnica.com/civis/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=421137&amp;sid=bc0216a5256140675548100709fda8f2">pallentx</a></span><span class="rank">Wise, Aged Ars Veteran</span>
      <aside class="icons">
        
        <a href="http://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2014/03/how-the-worlds-first-bitcoin-bank-was-robbed-blind/?comments=1&post=26369895#comment-26369895" title="2014-03-05T11:14:08-06:00" class="timeago datetime">Wed Mar 05, 2014 11:14 am</a>
        
